{"tid":152373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李少光:警務處長不需為七警案道歉　若在美國警察已開槍　要道歉的是示威者","createTime":"2017-03-11T16:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T20:02:31.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":69,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"81a621219654a4fa3ea7d7ed9e601d555193fb14","tid":152373,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T16:46:59.000Z","msg":"電台引述李少光：一哥不需為七警案道歉　若在美國警察已開槍<br />\n2017/3/10 &mdash; 15:23<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Screen20Shot202017-03-1020at203.39.0020PM20220copy_QAkql_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FScreen20Shot202017-03-1020at203.39.0020PM20220copy_QAkql_1200x0.png&h=779be39c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n身處北京的港區人大代表、前保安局長李少光，今日回應對七警案的看法。他認為警務處處長盧偉聰不需要七警案向公眾道歉，反指要道歉的應該是示威者。<br />\n<br />\n李少光指出，七警反應過激牴觸法律是事實，但他們都是在受到挑釁下，才作出過激行為。他又認為應設身處地想，假如市民被挑釁及淋尿液會如何，又說如果在美國警察已經開槍。<br />\n<br />\n他支持成立辱警罪，不認為此舉會令警民關係火上加油，至於如何界定辱警應由立法會議員決定。他指警察工作盡心盡力，但現時有市民濫用示威權利，不少警員尊嚴受損、身體受傷，長此下去非香港之福。李少光承認有向協助受佔領行動影響警員的「敬言仁基金」捐款，但拒絕透露金額。<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/電台引述李少光-一哥不須為七警案道歉-若在美國警察已開槍/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%9B%BB%E5%8F%B0%E5%BC%95%E8%BF%B0%E6%9D%8E%E5%B0%91%E5%85%89-%E4%B8%80%E5%93%A5%E4%B8%8D%E9%A0%88%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%83%E8%AD%A6%E6%A1%88%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89-%E8%8B%A5%E5%9C%A8%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%B7%B2%E9%96%8B%E6%A7%8D%2F&d=30ZlKbyCH33W3wkrfz60C7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=8b77ea91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%9B%BB%E5%8F%B0%E5%BC%95%E8%BF%B0%E6%9D%8E%E5%B0%91%E5%85%89-%E4%B8%80%E5%93%A5%E4%B8%8D%E9%A0%88%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%83%E8%AD%A6%E6%A1%88%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89-%E8%8B%A5%E5%9C%A8%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%B7%B2%E9%96%8B%E6%A7%8D%2F&h=532c0322\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/電台引述李少光-一哥不須為七警案道歉-若在美國警察已開槍/</a>"},{"pid":"c9cb6dee9a45d73ab0b74d5cd7f366e3d46769e8","tid":152373,"uid":37430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T16:50:40.000Z","msg":"美國美國成撚日都講美國<br />\n<br />\n又唔見你比香港人買槍？"},{"pid":"7dba5d0cceb02a5cebc609e812a7dc0fa2d96dfe","tid":152373,"uid":1510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T16:51:38.000Z","msg":"如果有美國咁嘅示威 又燒車又燃燒彈 我認為開槍正常  但可惜香港唔係"},{"pid":"1b552b102a792fd52774fa41c7dbae7e497f0e0a","tid":152373,"uid":1510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T16:52:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美國美國成撚日都講美國<br />\n<br />\n又唔見你比香港人買槍？</blockquote><br />\n廢老口吻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果係美國，一早xxxxx"},{"pid":"895d6db39b08922b04ec1ada42fbb9f103e4be1d","tid":152373,"uid":20659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T16:53:15.000Z","msg":"美國駐港領事館應該要出聲屌柒佢"},{"pid":"698dd4ae7f1a6aa3ce470ee498a8caf3ecc092a8","tid":152373,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T16:53:35.000Z","msg":"試下開槍，講到美國差佬開槍打個示威者，係合法嘅，人地美國無法無天嘅咁咪謀殺囉！點止坐兩年呀"},{"pid":"da9294dd6a79461e0edeeb5a84369699da4c33fd","tid":152373,"uid":340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T16:54:05.000Z","msg":"幾時比港人合法買炮先"},{"pid":"2d1929180cd37196ea41fe63d0c2092b968802ca","tid":152373,"uid":6818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T16:55:20.000Z","msg":"Address: 26 Garden Road, Central, Hong Kong<br />\nTel: (852) 2523-9011<br />\n(Please note that U.S. citizen and visa inquiries will not be answered on this line)<br />\nFax: (852) 2845-1598<br />\n係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不如寫信去美國領事館問吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n英文好嘅巴打幫手寫封信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ador